openhexagon
===========
Open Hexagon requires some manual setup before first use.

The following will get everything set up:
$ mkdir -p ~/.config/openhexagon
$ cp ${TRUEPREFIX}/share/examples/openhexagon/{config,scores,users}.json \
	~/.config/openhexagon
